                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7581" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1194</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2555 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕巢幕上：小鹏汽车能否扭亏为盈？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A Swallow Nesting on A Canopy: Can Xiaopeng Turn Losses into Profits？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐俐，李金蔚，方燚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小鹏汽车</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小鹏汽车；成本管理；新能源汽车；降本增效</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xiaopeng; Cost Management; New Energy Vehicles; Cost Reduction and Efficiency Increase</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近几年，中国新能源汽车产业加速发展。新产品、新技术、新模式层出不穷，带动整个产业链突飞猛进地提升。但是，由于受到新冠疫情的冲击，新能源汽车市场形势不容乐观，小鹏汽车作为国内造车新势力的一员，也面临着前所未有的挑战。2022年8月23日小鹏汽车公布了第二季财报，财报显示企业增收但不增利，净亏损进一步扩大。本案例首先描述了小鹏汽车发展至今的辉煌之路，其次总结了小鹏汽车造成净亏损的原因以及小鹏汽车为应对此次困境所采取的一系列积极措施。通过对相关问题的思考，学习并掌握相关成本管理的理论知识，深入分析当企业深陷财务困境时，企业该做出怎样的决策。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, China&#39;s new energy vehicle industry has accelerated its development. New products, new technologies and new models emerge in endlessly, driving the whole industrial chain to improve by leaps and bounds. However, due to the impact of the novel coronavirus epidemic, the market situation of new energy vehicles is not optimistic. Xiaopeng, as a member of the new force of domestic car manufacturing, is also facing unprecedented challenges. On August 23, 2022, Xiaopeng announced the second quarter financial results, the financial results showed that the enterprise increased revenue but did not increase profit, and the net loss further expanded. This case first describes the brilliant road of the development of Xiaopeng, and then summarizes the reasons for the net loss of Xiaopeng and a series of positive measures taken by Xiaopeng to deal with the predicament. By thinking about relevant issues, learning and mastering the theoretical knowledge of cost management, in-depth analysis of what decisions enterprises should make when they are in financial trouble.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《成本管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“成本管理理论”;“成本控制理论”；“成本管理方法”。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
